subject: This is not a job search list

messageBody:
Everyone:

There have been a large number of job-related e-mails coming into this
list. I am routinely removing the poster and deleting the e-mail. This
is not a job search list, either for employees or employers. If you want
to find a job, use another venue. (xp-jobs, for example)

Please stop wasting my time posting job ads, particularly if you are
only looking for candidates in one region of the world. North Americans,
by and large, do not care about jobs in India; and I imagine that's true
the other way around.

Thank you.
--
J. B. Rainsberger,
Diaspar Software Services
